    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Description</h2><strong>Electraplanet </strong>is a <strong>survival/adventure</strong> game. Using third-person point of view, you can explore new planets after your’s has been exploited entirely. <strong>Fighting and exploring</strong> are the main key’s to start your own electricity factory or upgrade your production levels.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704590/extras/6f9a08b845b75f0038b40710a808b655.poster.avif?t=1637581338\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704590/extras/6f9a08b845b75f0038b40710a808b655.webm?t=1637581338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704590/extras/6f9a08b845b75f0038b40710a808b655.mp4?t=1637581338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Grow</h2><strong>Produce</strong>, <strong>Protect </strong>your electricity and <strong>optimize </strong>your production, since <strong>electricity </strong>is the <strong>currency</strong>. With a exponential progression, the more you produce, the more you are <strong>efficient</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704590/extras/2e98c9c5db2281d56342625723d17acb.poster.avif?t=1637581338\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704590/extras/2e98c9c5db2281d56342625723d17acb.webm?t=1637581338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704590/extras/2e98c9c5db2281d56342625723d17acb.mp4?t=1637581338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Multiplayer Option</h2>An <strong>open world</strong> where you can create your <strong>strategy </strong>with your <strong>friends </strong>by simply starting a game or continuing your older one, and friends <strong>can join through Steam</strong>. Sharing <strong>creations</strong>, <strong>fight </strong>become really <strong>interesting with friends</strong>!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704590/extras/a0ca4bef65f532ad5c07125677170537.poster.avif?t=1637581338\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704590/extras/a0ca4bef65f532ad5c07125677170537.webm?t=1637581338\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1704590/extras/a0ca4bef65f532ad5c07125677170537.mp4?t=1637581338\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
